<refsect2>
<title><anchor id="gdk-gl-font-use-pango-font" role="function"/>gdk_gl_font_use_pango_font ()</title>
<indexterm><primary>gdk_gl_font_use_pango_font</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="PangoFont">PangoFont</link>*  gdk_gl_font_use_pango_font      (const <link linkend="PangoFontDescription">PangoFontDescription</link> *font_desc,
                                             <link linkend="int">int</link> first,
                                             <link linkend="int">int</link> count,
                                             <link linkend="int">int</link> list_base);</programlisting>
<para>
Creates bitmap display lists from a <link linkend="PangoFont"><type>PangoFont</type></link>.</para>
<para>

</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>font_desc</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> a <link linkend="PangoFontDescription"><type>PangoFontDescription</type></link> describing the font to use.
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>first</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the index of the first glyph to be taken.
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>count</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the number of glyphs to be taken.
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>list_base</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the index of the first display list to be generated.
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&nbsp;:</term><listitem><simpara> the <link linkend="PangoFont"><type>PangoFont</type></link> used, or NULL if no font matched.
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist></refsect2>
